<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>81</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<title>Migilo Sika Thi</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van in tuipi gal lam,
 Gamla taka mangsate hawl din;
 Mi gilo sika thi di'n,
 Van Lal cha ngei a hun sawl ui,
 Aw mi-dang a thei a um puou maw?

[V2]
 Aw, lawpin nuomin ka tha liengthei,
 Na manna chu thuk mahleh;
 Paradis-ah A hun tun tai,
 Aw gamla taka hun Hawlpa khan

[V3]
 2. Ka sik in a thi a ,
 Aw ka sik in a zep thidup ui;
 Bawhsepa banga ngai in,
 Mi dikpa chu a thawksak ui,
 Aw A thihna ah kei ka hing tai.

[V4]
 3. Mi lungkham gen leuhing,
 Lal Isu kheltha thei a um dem?
 Aw hehpihna, ziek chauh a,
 Khawul thisan guola va hi,
 Aw sim le mal ah hawlviel tiemu.

[V5]
 4. Thisan lun Thisan lun,
 Aw van Lal cha ngei thisan lun chu;
 Gitloh leh dogal kalah,
 Hinna kawpi a tung dawktai,
 Aw van chun athan asuoh ta ie.</lyrics>
</song>